title: HelloHero: Double Asian Pork & Veggie Stir-Fry with Udon Noodles & Crushed Peanuts
description: Sure, we've been accused of being a little nutty. So what? When the results are as quick and delicious as these warm pork
noodles with plenty of tasty crunch from the crushed peanuts, we'll wear the nutty badge with pride!
We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with broccoli due to local
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!
